        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="product-tabs">
        <div class="tab-nav">
          <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="switchTab('details', this)">Product Details</button>
          <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('ingredients', this)">Ingredients</button>
          <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('usage', this)">How to Use</button>
          <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('delivery', this)">Delivery</button>
        </div>

        <div class="tab-panel active" id="tab-details">
          <p>Energy Vitality Capsules are formulated with adaptogenic herbs and natural vitamins that help your body manage energy levels efficiently. This premium product is ideal for anyone experiencing tiredness, low energy, or needing extra support for an active lifestyle.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Form: Capsules</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Pack size: 60 capsules</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Category: Supplement</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Suitable for: Adults 18+</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="tab-panel" id="tab-ingredients">
          <p>Made with adaptogenic herbs and natural energy-supporting nutrients. No caffeine, no artificial stimulants.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><i class="fas fa-leaf"></i> Ashwagandha root extract</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-leaf"></i> Maca root powder</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-leaf"></i> B-vitamin complex</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-leaf"></i> Iron</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-leaf"></i> Ginseng extract</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="tab-panel" id="tab-usage">
          <p>Take 2 capsules daily with water, preferably in the morning with breakfast. For best results, use consistently for at least 4 weeks.</p>
          <p>Not recommended for pregnant or breastfeeding women. Consult your doctor if you are on any medication.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="tab-panel" id="tab-delivery">
          <p>We deliver across Rwanda. Orders are processed within 24 hours and delivered within 2–4 business days.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><i class="fas fa-truck"></i> Free delivery on all orders</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-undo"></i> 30-day money back guarantee</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> Call us on +250 788 333 339 to track your order</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i> Or dial *123# from your phone</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="related-section">
